[1.191366, "o", "---\r\ntype: synthesis\r\nupdated: \u001b[1m2026\u001b[0m-\u001b[1m07\u001b[0m-\u001b[1m04\u001b[0m\r\nsource_count: \u001b[1m2\u001b[0m\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Synthesis\r\n\r\n## Thesis\r\n\r\nThe LLM Wiki pattern replaces ephemeral RAG retrieval with a **compounding \r\nmarkdown wiki** that an agent maintains. Knowledge is compiled during ingest and\r\nstays current through lint passes вҖ” not re-derived on every question.\r\n\r\n## Revised insight \u001b[1m(\u001b[0mafter qmd source\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nStructured wikis and search are **layered, not either/or**. Karpathy's pattern \r\nkeeps bookkeeping in markdown \u001b[1m(\u001b[0mentities, synthesis, contradictions\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m. Lexical \r\n`wiki search` suffices early; when paraphrased queries miss distant pages, add \r\n"]
[1.199372, "o", "\r\n"]
[1.199429, "o", "в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\r\n Done. Open examples/demo/ in Obsidian for the graph view.\r\n Next: cp your-file.md /Users/cobusgreyling/llm-wiki/examples/demo/raw/ && ask your agent to ingest.\r\n"]
